The DRC-Africa Business Forum 2021 started with a bang on Wednesday, November 24 in the Congolese capital, Kinshasa. The theme of the forum was the "Economic Integration of the Congolese in the Value Chain of the Electric Battery Industry through Innovative Financial Solutions." A battery of firm commitments was signed by the various stakeholders to bring about the development of a battery minerals industry in the Democratic Republic of Congo two years from now. FRENCH coverage: Des engagements signés pour une industrie des batteries électriques en RDC